parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the engine to stall, leading to loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ignition switch slips into the off mode while the vehicle is running
the engine stalls without warning
the electrical system fails
and the brake and check engine warning lights illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the engine to stall, leading to loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The electrical system fails
the instrument panel quits working
no power steering
brakes
or lights
and the vehicle stalls without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding door can cause the door to open or close unexpectedly, which can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power sliding door opens or closes unexpectedly
the door chime does not stop
and the door will not close properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heated seat can cause burns or fires, which can increase the risk of injuries.
symptoms: The heated seat gets extremely hot
causing burns or fires.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear hatch can cause injury or death if it falls unexpectedly, and can also lead to accidents if it obstructs the driver's view.
symptoms: The rear hatch drops or falls unexpectedly
the hatch does not stay open
the hatch makes a sudden noise or movement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding doors can cause injury or death if they open or close unexpectedly, and can also lead to accidents if they obstruct the driver's view or distract the driver.
symptoms: The sliding doors open or close unexpectedly
the doors do not latch properly
the doors make a sudden noise or movement
the doors do not respond to the remote control or door handle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust issue on the chassis can cause the rear wheel and its components to break free, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: The chassis has excessive rust
the rear wheel and its components break free
the vehicle is difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Opening of Power Sliding Doors
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended opening of the power sliding doors can cause accidents, injuries, or leave children or pets unattended, and also leads to theft or loss of personal belongings.
symptoms: The power sliding doors open unexpectedly
sometimes while the vehicle is in motion
and may not close properly
causing the door ajar alarm to sound continuously.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Power Sliding Door Latches and Motors
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding door latches and motors can cause the doors to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The power sliding doors do not close or open properly
may get stuck
or make abnormal sounds
and the door ajar alarm may sound continuously.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Safety Features of Power Sliding Doors
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate safety features of the power sliding doors can cause injuries, especially to children, as the doors may not detect obstacles or retract when an object is in the way.
symptoms: The power sliding doors do not have a safety mechanism to detect obstacles or retract when an object is in the way
and may pinch or trap fingers.
